sectors;</p></list-item><list-item id="id-51ee21bd-95ac-4cec-d81a-eed2077b9555"><p>Awareness-raising of the local population by organizing roundtable discussions,</p></list-item><list-item id="id-75ae6913-72b4-4736-b038-98d0b5beae1a"><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="ccf51e04-6326-4b0b-8b38-9a3d81e7ddce"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="6fe69996-e4fc-434a-984c-0b63bd1ec650" text="[proposed modification following GB 737:] C" timestamp="1675426881727"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="01eaeede-d564-4c55-cab8-f4276e2f4294" timestamp="1675426883784"?>C<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="01eaeede-d564-4c55-cab8-f4276e2f4294"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="d31b9720-20a1-4f20-f8e0-57b2d73a0f8c" timestamp="1666960332210"?>reating and disseminating animated educational c<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="d31b9720-20a1-4f20-f8e0-57b2d73a0f8c"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="830bc787-1e12-458a-8f44-f56ff88054d1" text="ontent" timestamp="1671526382417"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="5af72503-7ceb-4e45-b65d-0256a716f5e8" timestamp="1671526383026"?>omic<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="5af72503-7ceb-4e45-b65d-0256a716f5e8"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="a5b1036a-068a-4ae7-a911-599a35fb56c5" timestamp="1666960332210"?> (e.g. <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="a5b1036a-068a-4ae7-a911-599a35fb56c5"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="af90b467-3de8-4049-fc16-ae4c3f0aaf27" timestamp="1668697812650"?>Gender <?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="af90b467-3de8-4049-fc16-ae4c3f0aaf27"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="d42d12f7-6e4f-4a9c-84e2-414beaaba1e5" timestamp="1666960332210"?>manga), and providing gender education at school.</p></list-item><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="d42d12f7-6e4f-4a9c